defaultFor the purposes of the Regulations, a properly incorporated UK subsidiary of a firm is a UK firm. 
defaultThis means that
default UK based subsidiaries or groups of multinational firms would count as being UK based.
default It is therefore
default 
defaultdebateable as to the extent that money 
defaultis flowing out of the UK economy.
