default A best value authority must make arrangements to secure 
defaultcontinuous improvement
default in the way in which its func
defaulttions are exercised, having regard to a combination of economy, efficiency and effectiveness (LGA 1999, section 3[1]).  A list of best value authorities can be found at 
defaulthttp://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1999/27/section/1
